            "style": "",
            "text": ", resulting in some truly unique outcomes. And while this bike doesn’t exist, it’s not unheard of for a digital sketch such as this to be transformed into a fully-functional ride for discerning, well-heeled customers. If any automaker is crazy enough to do such a thing, it’s Bugatti.",
