          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "After taking a break from the project, Pieper decided to revisit it. For the second go-around, he went with a three-dimensional model and put the bike in the scenery of the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
