      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The light blue on the nose of this superbike is supposed to be a callback to classic Bugatti racecars from the 1930s. Same goes for the air vents toward the bottom-front on both sides and the chrome fuel cap.",
