      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Another modern detail is the carbon-fiber frame, which you see clearly in the rear. Just like with other modern land speed record-setting superbikes, the wheels are pushed wheel out in front and behind the seat and fuel tank to add stability when this thing really gets going.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
